                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-23-off136 t18230625-23-crimeloc138"></join>, eighteen yards of woollen cloth, value 20 l., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18230625-23-victim252" type="victimName">
                        John Bowles 
                        Lucombe
                     <interp inst="t18230625-23-victim252" type="surname" value="Lucombe"></interp>
